item.title: Yahoo Chat
item.description: This chat log was cut short by technical difficulties (dialup connection crashed). Despite promises to provide the full log, Yahoo! never did. “CSI” star Jorja Fox It’s got to be a fabulous Spring for actress Jorja Fox. She’s in the coolest TV show of the season — CSI: Crime Scene Investigation — and one of the most talked about movies of the year — Memento. But you know, the last few years couldn’t have sucked… In the 99-00 season, she portrayed Secret Service Special Agent Gina Toscano on The West Wing, protecting President Bartlet’s youngest daughter.
